# format:
# [export path] [user/ip address,another user/another ip address] (options)
#
# supported option:
#	ro - read-only export
#	user=[username] - lower privileges to specified user (for this export only)
#
# example:
# /tmp 	127.0.0.1, alex, 10.0.0.2
# /tmp 	127.0.0.1, alex, 10.0.0.2 (ro)
# /tmp 	127.0.0.1, alex, 10.0.0.2 (ro,user=alex)

